    STIG-ID         : WN11-CC-000190
    Documentation   : https://stigaview.com/products/win11/v2r7/WN11-CC-000190/
.TESTED ON
    Date(s) Tested  : 
    Tested By       : 
    Systems Tested  : 
    PowerShell Ver. : 
.USAGE
    Put any usage instructions here.
    Example syntax:
    PS C:\> .\__remediation_template(STIG-ID-WN11-CC-000190).ps1 
